{
  "name": "CONCLUSION-page",
  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "name": "ConclusionPanel",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "ConclusionHeading",
          "html": "<h3>Conclusions</h3>"
        },

        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionsPanelLifeStatusTrue",
          "visibleIf": "{LifeStatus} = true",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "Conclusion",
              "html": "<p>The final section of this survey asks questions about the last station of {CmpnName}'s LP/GOLPP journey before {genderSubjectPronoun} crossed over the Rainbow Bridge. If it's too painful to revisit this stage of {CmpnName}'s life, it might be best to discontinue the survey and return to it later. </p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "Conclusion",
              "html": "<p>This section references questions you asked earlier in the survey to get a picture of how {CmpnName}'s LP/GOLPP changed over time in relation to other factors that played a role in {CmpnName}'s LP/GOLPP journey. </p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionsPanelLifeStatusFalse",
          "visibleIf": "{LifeStatus} = false",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "Conclusion",
              "html": "<p>The last survey section asks questions about the current state of {CmpnName}'s LP/GOLPP. By comparing your answers here to answers you provided earlier, we hope to get a picture of how {genderObjectPronoun} condition changed over time and what factors may have played a role in the LP/GOLPP progression</p>"
            }
    
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "ConclusionIntro",
          "html": "<p><b>NOTE:</b> The questions in this final section pertain to {CmpnName} {blobText}:</p>"
        },  

        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionDetailsPanel",
          "elements": [


            {
              "type": "checkbox",
              "name": "ConclusionSpecialConsiderations",
              "title": "Please describe any special considerations for {CmpnName} due to LP-related breathing issues:",
              "isRequired": true,
              "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "NO_CONSIDERATIONS",
                  "text": "No special considerations"
                },
                {
                  "value": "EXERCISE",
                  "text": "Exercise limitations"
                },
                {
                  "value": "FOOD",
                  "text": "Type, amount or frequency of feeding"
                },
                {
                  "value": "TRAVEL",
                  "text": "Travel restrictions"
                },
                {
                  "value": "EXCITEMENT",
                  "text": "Other behavior restrictions i.e., anxiety, excitement"
                }
              ],
              "showOtherItem": true
            },
            {
              "type": "checkbox",
              "name": "ConclusionPolyneuropathy",
              "title": "Please describe {CmpnName}'s polyneuropathy:",
              "isRequired": true,
              "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "NO_SYMPTOMS",
                  "text": "No noticeable symptoms"
                },
                {
                  "value": "HIND_END",
                  "text": "Significant hind-end weakness"
                },
                {
                  "value": "FALLING",
                  "text": "Frequent falling"
                },
                {
                  "value": "GET_UP",
                  "text": "Difficulty getting up or standing"
                },
                {
                  "value": "URINARY",
                  "text": "Urinary incontinence"
                },
                {
                  "value": "FECAL",
                  "text": "Fecal incontinence"
                }
              ],
              "showOtherItem": false
            },
            {
              "type": "rating",
              "name": "ConclusionQOL",
              "title": "How would you rate {CmpnName}'s quality of life at this stage?",
              "description": "1 = very poor, 3 = fair, 5 = very good",
              "isRequired": true,
              "rateValues": [
                { "value": 1, "text": "1" },
                { "value": 2, "text": "2" },
                { "value": 3, "text": "3" },
                { "value": 4, "text": "4" },
                { "value": 5, "text": "5" },
                { "value": "DONT_KNOW", "text": "Don't know" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },


        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionOtherConditionsPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
            "type": "checkbox",
            "name": "ConclusionOtherConditions",
            "title": "What other conditions {doTense} {CmpnName} have at this stage?",
            "description": "Your selections here will be compared to earlier answers to deterimine which of these conditions developed during {CmpnName}'s LP/GOLPP journey.",
            "isRequired": true,
            "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "GERD",
                  "text": "Acid reflux (GERD)"
                },
                {
                  "value": "ME",
                  "text": "Megaesophagus"
                },
                {
                  "value": "DM",
                  "text": "Degenerative Myelopathy"
                },
                {
                  "value": "ARTHRITIS",
                  "text": "Arthritis"
                },
                {
                  "value": "CUSHINGS",
                  "text": "Cushings"
                },
                {
                  "value": "CT",
                  "text": "Collapsing Trachea"
                },
                {
                  "value": "HYPOTHYROID",
                  "text": "Hypothyroidism"
                },
                {
                  "value": "HEMANGIOSARCOMA",
                  "text": "Hemangiosarcoma"
                }
              ],
              "choicesOrder": "none",
              "otherText": "Other (max. 250 characters)",
              "showOtherItem": true
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionCauseOfDeathPanel",
          "visibleIf": "{LifeStatus} = true",
          "elements": [
              {
                "type": "html",
                "name": "ConclusionCauseOfDeathHeading",
                "html": "Euthanasia is a humane way to say goodbye when a beloved animal companion has reached end-of-life. This questions asks about the primary cause of {CmpnName}'s passing, not whether humane euthanasia was chosen to help them cross over."
              },
              {
                "type": "radiogroup",
                "name": "ConclusionCauseOfDeath",
                "title": "What was the ultimate reason why {CmpnName} crossed over the Rainbow Bridge?",
                "isRequired": true,
                "choices": [
                  {
                    "value": "COMPLICATIONS",
                    "text": "Direct post-operative complications of LP surgery or stent implant"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "BREATHING_CRISIS",
                    "text": "LP-related breathing crisis"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "CANCER",
                    "text": "Cancer"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "INFECTION",
                    "text": "Bacterial/viral infection"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "ADVANCED_POLYNEUROPATHY",
                    "text": "Polyneuropathy/cognitive decline"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "SEIZURE",
                    "text": "Seizure or stroke"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "STOPPED_EATING",
                    "text": "Stopped eating"
                  }
                ],
                "showOtherItem": true,
                "otherText": "Other issues"
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "ConclusionLastQuestion",
          "title": "Survey Conclusion",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "ConclusionLastQuestionIntro",
              "html": "LP/GOLPP is a merciless, ruthless disease that forces us to make impossible decisions for our beloved companions. The last question of this survey is speculative. If you were to have another dog with LP, would you choose a different path along their LP/GOLPP journey?"
            }
            
          ]
        }









      ]
    }
  ]
}